00:03:58.020 --> 00:04:01.660
you can see the F key being pressed on the keyboard.

57
00:04:01.660 --> 00:04:06.260
So we can see event begin play on the left hand side and F as they're both inputs that

58
00:04:06.260 --> 00:04:09.120
fire during runtime.

59
00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:13.100
You've got your functions that live here and your construction script, which we'll be going

